				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Is getting the Scepter Frame in Akheva Ruins bard-soloable?<a name="30280"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 24 04 3:41 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I've seen a handful of strategies on how the turnins needed for the Scepter Frame (for the VT Key quest) can be soloed by certain other classes.  What I'm wondering is, is it doable by a solo Bard?  Specifically, a 65/60 Bard with FM?
<br />

<br />
It looks like there's an AWFUL lot of things to lull.
<br />

<br />
Has anyone here ever actually done it?</span></td>
