				<td colspan="2"><span>I soloed the frame... infact i soloed allmost all the shards as well, heres what you want to do, selos out side of AR, zone in and invis to the spot and train there if nessarty, then run to where the sarcifices spawn and do 1 burst of melody of misthef this will DoT and kill all 4 at once, once the burst lands turn off the song, run out of the room and fade in the right conor thats free of wanders, now you have 2 options from this point, you can wait for the mobs to respawn in the room, as theres a safe spot where none of the static spawns will aggro at ( its to the right of the room faceing the sacrifical mobs near the left starcase and foward from the mobs in the very middle of the room its kinda tight but it is safe to med at), OR after fadeing run back out of AR reselos and repete if the mob isient on track, now once the named is up on track it gets a little fun, target the 1 of the 3 mobs at the top of the pit and sight bind on it, then twist 1 pulse of CHA song and lull all 3 mobs, you now have a 6-8 second aggro free window, turn in the essence emereld and collect the frame</span></td>
