				<td colspan="2"><span>I too soloed the frame turn in. It is very easy if you have fade.
<br />

<br />
I zoned in with selos chorus, and invised. I ran to the sacrificial pit room and took a hard right once inside, and faded. Still invis, I moved to stand in the sacrificial pit, my back pressed against the back wall. The mobs on top won't agro! I bellowed the remains to death. I got agro once from the robes standing in front of the pit but fade saved me. Once the turn in mob spawns, just do your hand ins and make a run for it. It's easier to get in with selos than run out without it. <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
